[Selected Troops Have Infinite/Full Health &amp; MP]
author=bungholio
description=This works by affecting anything you select, but if you unselect it, they no longer have infinite amounts. But I did find interesting offset things to mess with it.
More offsets:
0004 - 1 byte - alliance (ally/enemy/neither)
00 = ally
01 = enemy faction 1
02 = enemy faction 2
03 and up = neutral
0010 - 2 unsigned bytes - ghost time
0012 - 2 unsigned bytes - ghost time (with the icon, as if it were an applied effect like the rest)
0014 - 2 unsigned bytes - immobilized
0016 - 2 unsigned bytes - slowness from slime
0018 - 2 unsigned bytes - sleep
001a - 2 unsigned bytes - purple foam (curse? which would damage you over time like poison)
patch=1,EE,20193210,extended,0C03FFC0
